I"Y<h1 id="mark-robeck">Mark Robeck</h1>

<p><strong>Role:</strong> Contributor</p>

<p><strong>Position:</strong> Founder and President, Energy Evolution Consulting LLC</p>

<p><strong>Background:</strong><br />
Mark Robeck is an experienced energy lawyer and consultant, currently serving as the Founder and President of Energy Evolution Consulting LLC. With over 30 years of experience, Robeck has held significant roles in both the public and private sectors, including Deputy General Counsel for Energy Policy at the U.S. Department of Energy during the Trump administration. Prior to his government service, he co-led energy practices at major law firms, providing legal counsel on a wide range of energy-related issues.</p>

<p><strong>Relation to Trump:</strong><br />
Robeck’s role as Deputy General Counsel at the Department of Energy placed him at the center of the Trump administration’s energy policies, where he advised on various energy and environmental regulations.</p>

<p><strong>Scandals or Controversies:</strong><br />
There are no significant scandals associated with Mark Robeck.</p>

